== PVP-Arena

A PVP experience enhancing plugin.

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

=== Features

* Multiple arenas
* Battlefield regions
* Customizable classes
* Player-state saving
* Arena regions
* In-game configuration access
* Arena disable
* Leader boards
* Spawn protection
* Flag coloring
* Inventory drops
* Announcements
* Arena end timer

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

=== Functions

* Enhancing PVP experience

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

=== Dependencies

* CraftBukkit Beta 1.3.2-R2.0

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

=== How to install

* Place in plugins folder
* Place arena files in /pvparena/files
* Configure if you wish to
* Done!

